OL,3,CAir India crash: Relatives of victims
OL,4,Cstill searching for answers one year on
OL,6,FThe hardest thing, Miten Patel tells
OL,7,Fme, is answering questions from his
OL,8,Fyoung children.
OL,10,F"Where are they?" they ask about their
OL,11,Fgrandparents' sudden absence. "Are
OL,12,Fthey upset with us?"
OL,14,FAshok and Shobhna Patel were among the
OL,15,F241 people killed when Air India
OL,16,FFlight 171 crashed in one of the worst
OL,17,Faviation disasters involving British
OL,18,Fcitizens in recent years.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@QO]sD@_OUtD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
