OL,3,CAir India crash: Relatives of victims
OL,4,Cstill searching for answers one year on
OL,6,FOn 12 June, 2025, the flight from
OL,7,FAhmedabad to London Gatwick plunged to
OL,8,Fthe ground less than a minute after
OL,9,Ftake-off.
OL,11,FMr and Mrs Patel, who were returning
OL,12,Fhome to Orpington in south-east
OL,13,FLondon, were among the 53 Britons who
OL,14,Fdied.
OL,16,FA year later, the cause of the crash
OL,17,Fremains unknown. Families are still
OL,18,Fmourning and still asking what
OL,19,Fhappened ` and why.
OL,21,FMiten is one of them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
