OL,3,CAir India crash: Relatives of victims
OL,4,Cstill searching for answers one year on
OL,6,FWhen I meet him at home, he says he is
OL,7,Fno closer to the answers he
OL,8,Fdesperately wants. He is calling on
OL,9,Finvestigators to publish their final
OL,10,Freport.
OL,12,F"There's been no transparency, so much
OL,13,Fmiscommunication, so many experts and
OL,14,Ftheories - it just confuses people."
OL,16,FFamilies, he says, are "looking for
OL,17,Faccountability and answers" but "do
OL,18,Fnot get updates regarding the crash
OL,19,Ffrom anyone".
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@dO]xD@XOUyD@[O]yD@aOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
