OL,3,CAir India crash: Relatives of victims
OL,4,Cstill searching for answers one year on
OL,6,FThe last update on Flight 171
OL,7,Fpublished on Air India's website was
OL,8,Fin July 2025 - eleven months ago.
OL,10,FA month after the crash, Indian
OL,11,Fauthorities released a preliminary
OL,12,Freport, in line with standard
OL,13,Fprocedure.
OL,15,FIt found that both fuel control
OL,16,Fswitches moved to the "cut-off"
OL,17,Fposition immediately after take-off,
OL,18,Fstopping fuel from reaching the
OL,19,Fengines.
OL,21,FWhy that happened remains unknown.
OL,26,@xD@WOUxD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
