OL,3,CAir India crash: Relatives of victims
OL,4,Cstill searching for answers one year on
OL,6,FThe questions keep him awake at night.
OL,7,FIn the absence of official answers, he
OL,8,Fhas searched for his own.
OL,10,FOnline, he found footage filmed by
OL,11,Fpassengers boarding the aircraft.
OL,13,FIn the background, he spotted his
OL,14,Fparents.
OL,16,FHe knows exactly where they were
OL,17,Fsitting, Row 37, and shows me images
OL,18,Fof his mother and father in their
OL,19,Ffinal moments.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
