OL,3,CAir India crash: Relatives of victims
OL,4,Cstill searching for answers one year on
OL,6,FThere is comfort in seeing them
OL,7,Flooking so happy.
OL,9,FThey were never meant to be on that
OL,10,Fflight. Originally due to return a
OL,11,Fweek later, they changed their plans
OL,12,Fto be home for Miten's wedding
OL,13,Fanniversary.
OL,15,FIt is now a date forever linked to
OL,16,Ftheir loss.
OL,18,FThe day after the crash, Miten
OL,19,Ftravelled to India to bring his
OL,20,Fparents home. But he says what
OL,21,Ffollowed raised even more questions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
