OL,3,CAir India crash: Relatives of victims
OL,4,Cstill searching for answers one year on
OL,6,FWhen his mother's casket arrived in
OL,7,Fthe UK, the coroner discovered that
OL,8,Fother human remains had been returned
OL,9,Falongside hers.
OL,11,FMiten says he was never given the
OL,12,Fopportunity to verify its contents
OL,13,Fbefore leaving India.
OL,15,FOnly last week, he met the coroner,
OL,16,Fwho confirmed all of his mother's
OL,17,Fremains had been recovered. But
OL,18,Fsubstantial remains belonging to
OL,19,Fanother victim had also been
OL,20,Fidentified and separated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
