OL,3,CAir India crash: Relatives of victims
OL,4,Cstill searching for answers one year on
OL,6,FMiten says he has repeatedly asked the
OL,7,FIndian authorities for information
OL,8,Fabout that person, but has received
OL,9,Fnone.
OL,11,F"They need to show compassion," he
OL,12,Fsays. "We're now one year on. These
OL,13,Fremains need to be returned to their
OL,14,Floved ones."
OL,16,FHe says similar cases have emerged
OL,17,Finvolving other families.
OL,19,FIn one case, he says, the remains of a
OL,20,Ffemale victim were sent to the UK
OL,21,Fdespite her family living in India.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@_O]tD@GOUvD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
