OL,3,CAir India crash: Relatives of victims
OL,4,Cstill searching for answers one year on
OL,6,FMiten shows me the fire-damaged
OL,7,Fpassports that belonged to his
OL,8,Fparents. The last time he held them
OL,9,Fwas at Gatwick Airport before they
OL,10,Fdeparted.
OL,12,FAlong with e-tickets and baggage tags,
OL,13,Fthey were returned only last month.
OL,15,FHe also has one of his mother's tops.
OL,16,FTo recover it, he says he had to
OL,17,Fprovide Air India with a photograph of
OL,18,Fher wearing it.
OL,20,FHe smiles. "I never liked that top,
OL,21,Fbut now it's special."
OL,26,@|D@LOU}D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
