OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781287881
OL,3,CAir India crash: Relatives of victims
OL,4,Cstill searching for answers one year on
OL,6,FOf two large suitcases, only a handful
OL,7,Fof belongings have been returned.
OL,9,F"There must be more." More than
OL,10,Fanything, he wants his parents' mobile
OL,11,Fphones back.
OL,13,FIt's not the devices themselves that
OL,14,Fmatter, but what they may contain `
OL,15,Fphotographs from his parents' final
OL,16,Ftrip together.
OL,18,FHe also worries about the future of
OL,19,Fthe crash site, where accommodation
OL,20,Fblocks for doctors and nurses were
OL,21,Fdestroyed or badly damaged.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781287881
OL,3,CAir India crash: Relatives of victims
OL,4,Cstill searching for answers one year on
OL,6,FRedevelopment plans make no mention of
OL,7,Fa memorial.
OL,9,F"Where's the dignity?" he asks. "I
OL,10,Fstill continue to fight while holding
OL,11,Fmy grief in."
OL,13,FI ask whether campaigning for answers
OL,14,Fhas stopped him from moving forward.
OL,15,F"I don't think we'll ever get closure,
OL,16,Fto be honest."
OL,18,FHe says he is no longer the person he
OL,19,Fwas a year ago.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@VO]qD@aOUsD@MO]wD@AOUxD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
