OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781287881
OL,3,CAir India crash: Relatives of victims
OL,4,Cstill searching for answers one year on
OL,6,FToday, the family will gather for
OL,7,Fprayers. But he admits he is
OL,8,Fstruggling with his faith. "I'll get
OL,9,Fit back. But right now, it's a
OL,10,Fstruggle."
OL,12,FAttempting to answer his children's
OL,13,Fquestions, he has used AI to create an
OL,14,Fimage of their grandparents sitting
OL,15,Fbeside them.
OL,17,FIt doesn't answer the questions they
OL,18,Fask.
OL,20,FBut for now, it's the closest thing to
OL,21,Fan answer he has.
OL,26,@pD@\OUrD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
