OL,3,CAir India crash: Relatives of victims
OL,4,Cstill searching for answers one year on
OL,6,FThe Indian Air Accidents Investigation
OL,7,FBureau said: "On this solemn occasion,
OL,8,Fthe Aircraft Accident Investigation
OL,9,FBureau (AAIB) expresses its deepest
OL,10,Fcondolences to the families and loved
OL,11,Fones of all those who lost their lives
OL,12,Fin the accident."
OL,14,FIt pointed to its preliminary report
OL,15,Fin July 2025 and said its "extensive
OL,16,Fand rigorous examination" continues
OL,17,Fand is currently being analysed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
