FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30916
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1781287881
OL,3,CAir India crash: Relatives of victims
OL,4,Cstill searching for answers one year on
OL,6,FIt said Air India "had remained in
OL,7,Fclose and regular contact with the
OL,8,Ffamilies... offering our full support
OL,9,Fduring this difficult time, either
OL,10,Fdirectly or through their legal
OL,11,Frepresentatives where they have chosen
OL,12,Fthis route, to ensure they are kept
OL,13,Finformed of any and all developments."
